name: forest_battle
label: Forest Battle Skirmish (4)
description: The Forest Battle map created by Stanislas Dolcini (stanislas69) and edited by Niek ten Brinke (niektb). This map was created to participate in Mapping Contest 16 hosted by the Council of Modders. The initial version (before it was being reworked by niektb) won the 1st prize. This is a four player map specially designed to prevent early rushing.
